title: #92Noon! 11a Hour 3/4 - NFL/Touting
description: The obsession with 40 times and speed during the combine leads to coaches overdrafting and putting faith in their ability to coach speedsters into NFL stars...does it work? Some music frivolity and NBA touts to finish the show!
